2:35:05 AM [express] POST /api/chat 200 in 4456ms :: {"answer":"The AI search launch is facing a couple of significant blockers that need to be addressed. The most pressing issue is the AWS EU region quota, which is crucial for deploying the service with full capacity. Additionally, there is a challenge with the OpenAI API rate limits, which affects the embeddings generation during peak hours. [1]\n- The OpenAI API rate limits are another blocker, as the current limit of 1 million tokens per minute is insufficient for full production load. Priya Patel is managing this issue, with a mitigation strategy involving Redis queue buffering and batch processing. [1]\n\nWould you like me to go deeper on timeline, owners, or risks?","bullets":[{"claim":"The AWS EU region quota is a major blocker, with a mitigation plan to deploy at reduced capacity if the quota is not approved by November 11. This issue is being escalated by Jordan Martinez, and a go/no-go decision is set for November 13 [9][16].","citations":[{"sourceId":"a756b8bd-5e46-4211-bb39-aac7c778889f","sourceVersionId":"ae9befda-f635-4043-bfc2-93da7c73daf0","chunkId":"f93be69e-3ade-4b30-a950-a21040340e35","charStart":1700,"charEnd":2700,"label":"Product_Roadmap_2025.pdf","title":"Product_Roadmap_2025.pdf","score":0.45112326976146283,"snippet":"ty:\tP1\t(Should\tHave)\nOwner:\tSearch\tTeam\nEffort:\t4\tweeks\nUser\tStory:\nAs\ta\tuser,\tI\twant\tto\tfilter\tsearch\tresults\tby\tdate,\tauthor,\tproject,\tand\ndocument\ttype.\nFilters\tto\tAdd:\t-\tDate\tr"}]},{"claim":"The OpenAI API rate limits are another blocker, as the current limit of 1 million tokens per minute is insufficient for full production load. Priya Patel is managing this issue, with a mitigation strategy involving Redis queue buffering and batch processing [16].","citations":[]}],"action":null,"needsClarification":true,"clarifyingQuestions":["Would you like me to go deeper on timeline, owners, or risks?"],"answer_text":"The AI search launch is facing a 